long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This absolutely sick extension plays a sound effect of your choice when you submit a quiz or assignment on Canvas. Default sound is "Everything is Awesome"! Let me know about any bugs in the reviews... I banged this out in one afternoon.

And while you're here, check out my absolutely sick website that counts down the time till our next day off from school... http://nextbreak.rf.gd/
